I have a Sapphire II am/fm radio that I want to install in a '65 bus.
The radio has several wires that I need some help to identify: 
 
1)One brown wire that is double stranded(two wires seamed together) comes
from the right side of the radio. 
2)On the left side of the radio is three single wires, two of them
are black and one is brown.

Can anybody help me identify what is what?
